<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL37">
<l>teḷivilāk kalaṅkal nīrcūḻ tiruvaraṅkaṅ kattu ḷōṅku</l>
<l>moḷiyuḷār tāmē yaṉṟē tantaiyun tāyu māvār</l>
<l>eḷiyatō raruḷu maṉṟē yeṉṟiṟat tempi rāṉār</l>
<l>aḷiyaṉam paiya leṉṉā rammavō koṭiya vāṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is indeed Him with a flourishing lustre inside Śrīraṅgam</l>
<l rend="indent">surrounded by the turbid, muddy water</l>
<l>Who is both [our] Father and Mother, right?</l>
<l>Is it not simple grace towards me [that I want Him to give]?</l>
<l>Our Lord will not say, ‘Our little fellow deserves [our] protection.’</l>
<l rend="indent">Amma! [Such] cruel nature!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
